# 🏓 Selkirk Paddle Borrow Program

This web-based system helps Selkirk Advocates and retail partners **track borrowed demo paddles** with ease. It includes a simple borrower form, an automated confirmation email, and a live dashboard to track borrow/return status.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Easy form for users to borrow paddles (photo, contact info, paddle model)
- ✅ Auto email confirmation with paddle and return details
- ✅ Return reminders sent automatically
- ✅ Shareable dashboard for tracking paddle status (borrowed vs returned)
- ✅ Built with Google Forms, Sheets, and Apps Script

