## 🧰 Tech Stack

- Google Forms – for borrower intake
- Google Sheets – for storing and displaying data
- Google Apps Script – for automation and email reminders
- GitHub – for version control and project sharing

---

## 📂 Files Included

- `paddleborrow.gs` – Google Apps Script for automation
- `README.md` – Project overview and documentation
- `/screenshots/` – Visual examples of form, email, and dashboard

